description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for Excel

App offers quizzes and tutorials  to help you learn Excel

App is continuously updated based on your feedback.Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.

App Tools include search .



Includes following tutorials:

Introduction,
Getting Started,
Working with Data I,
Working with Data II,
Working with Data III,
Toolbars I,
Toolbars II,
Toolbars III,
Toolbars IV,
Toolbars V,
Formatting I,
Formatting II,
Creating Dropdown List,
Hiding and Unhiding Columns in Excel,
How to Protect Data in Excel,
Excel Keyboard Shortcuts I,
Excel Keyboard Shortcuts II.


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on Working with Data,
Quiz on Toolbars,
Quiz on Keyboard Shortcuts.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
